/**
\page hardware_config Hardware & Comms Configuration

\section hardware_configuration Hardware Configuration

\li None

\section comms_config Comms Configuration for Control

The 336 has an ethernet port. Using the front panel it is simple to configure the IP address.

The software was developed using Ethernet comms. The serial port (via the USB connector), or the GPIB port were not tested.

**/
